============
GEPETO - Is a small Game Engine intended to help 
new developers understand how a game engine works.

It's still under development.

============

Features:
 - Supported system: Mac OS X 10.6 
 - OpenGL
 - Basic Rendering Engine
	- Shaders
	- Post Effect Shaders
 - Dae importer (.obj)

Still missing fratures:
 - Support to Windows XP/7
 - Memory Management
 - Strings
 - Math Library
 - Collections
 - File System Handlers
 - Clock
 - Physics
 - AI
 - Animation
 - Collada Importer (and remove the .obj importer)


